If we did such and such last night, would that be rad?

00:56:18.690 --> 00:56:19.650
Yeah.

00:56:20.770 --> 00:56:23.810
Freedom of information commission has occasionally

00:56:23.970 --> 00:56:27.650
spanked board members for doing something in violation of FOI.

00:56:28.205 --> 00:56:31.085
Their intent is never to punish a mistake.

00:56:31.245 --> 00:56:37.965
They don't wanna sit you know, we forgot to go back in a public session and and voted on something in executive session.

00:56:38.525 --> 00:56:44.830
Don't do that again. Just have put on the next agenda, voted over again. That's fine. They they want to help you do it right.

